data.description: Beautifully remodeled Patio Collection home in the renowned golf community of Spanish Trails. This property features everything you could possibly want... Porcelain tile throughout, rich laminate wood flooring, vaulted ceilings, updated kitchen including all stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, marble mosaic tile backsplash, formal dining room with a full mirrored wall and golf course views from every window. Enjoy the upstairs den area with a private balcony overlooking perfectly manicured greens. Shutters throughout the downstairs. Separate laundry room. Primary Bedroom located on the first floor for easy private access. Relax in your fully landscaped yard ON THE GOLF COURSE!! Community LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! This home sits directly across from the tennis courts and is walking distance to the pool and fitness center. Do not let this opportunity to have the best priced single family home in Spanish Trails pass you by. Make an appointment today!
